                    <note type="abstract" xml:id="abstract-en-1418">Pōsi and his daughter <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1370">Martha</persName> were Greeks deported to the
          Sasanian empire. They were martyred at Karka d-Ledan. Pōsi had been chief of the royal
          artisans.</note>
